<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<meta name="description" content="Composed — a soccer training companion for youth players who train between team sessions. Position-weighted progress. Counted from your footage. Coach-led pilots." />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0D0D0D" />
<title>Composed — Stop Guessing. Start Proving.</title>

<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><rect width='100' height='100' fill='%230D0D0D'/><text x='50' y='70' font-size='72' font-family='Georgia,serif' font-style='italic' font-weight='400' fill='%23F0EBE1' text-anchor='middle'>C</text></svg>" />

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0D0D0D;                          /* reference page bg */
    --bg-warm: #2A1A0A;                     /* brass-ember reveal (ball-lands-in-goal) */
    --bg-deep: #060606;
    --ink: #F0EBE1;                         /* ivory/bone — primary ink */
    --ink-soft: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.30);  /* body copy at rest */
    --ink-mute: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.55);
    --ink-quiet: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.12); /* ghost outlines */
    --accent: #C94A5C;                      /* coral emphasis — used sparingly */
    --brass: #C2A56B;                       /* existing Composed brass */
    --rim: rgba(74, 36, 16, 0.55);          /* warm rust vignette */
    --line: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.08);
    --line-soft: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.04);

    --serif: "Instrument Serif", ui-serif, Georgia, serif;
    --mono:  "DM Mono", ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    font-weight: 400;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    transition: background-color 900ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }
  body.warm-ground { background-color: var(--bg-warm); }
  ::selection { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); }
  img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  button { font: inherit; color: inherit; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
  :focus-visible { outline: 1px solid var(--ink); outline-offset: 4px; border-radius: 1px; }

  /* ── Atmospheric layers (fixed overlays) ── */
  .grain {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 400;
    opacity: 0.12;
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='320' height='320'><filter id='n'><feTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='2' stitchTiles='stitch'/><feColorMatrix values='0 0 0 0 0.94  0 0 0 0 0.92  0 0 0 0 0.88  0 0 0 0.55 0'/></filter><rect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/></svg>");
    background-size: 320px 320px;
  }
  .vignette {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 401;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 180px 12px var(--rim), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(74,36,16,0.35);
  }
  body.warm-ground .vignette { box-shadow: inset 0 0 180px 12px rgba(193,145,74,0.35), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(193,145,74,0.25); }

  /* ── Right-edge persistent pill (jump to pilot CTA) ── */
  .edge-pill {
    position: fixed; right: 0; top: 42%;
    z-index: 60;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 1rem 0.65rem 2.2rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-orientation: mixed;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 2px 0 0 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    transition: transform 0.28s ease;
  }
  .edge-pill:hover { transform: translateX(-3px); }
  .edge-pill .pill-key {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  /* ── Floating circular "scroll" badge ── */
  .scroll-badge {
    position: fixed;
    top: 2.2rem; left: 2.2rem;
    z-index: 55;
    width: 92px; height: 92px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.78;
    transition: opacity 0.45s ease, transform 0.45s ease;
  }
  .scroll-badge.fade { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); }
  .scroll-badge .sb-ring { animation: sbSpin 28s linear infinite; transform-origin: 46px 46px; }
  .scroll-badge text {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    fill: var(--ink-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .scroll-badge .sb-arrow {
    stroke: var(--ink);
    stroke-width: 1;
    fill: none;
  }
  @keyframes sbSpin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  /* ── Top nav (tiny) ── */
  nav.top {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 50;
    padding: 1.6rem clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  nav.top > * { pointer-events: auto; }
  nav.top .logo {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  nav.top .logo em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  nav.top .nav-contact {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    padding: 0.55rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  nav.top .nav-contact:hover { color: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink-mute); }

  /* ── Typography system ── */
  .display-hero {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(3.8rem, 10vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }
  .display-hero .serif-it { font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; }
  .chapter-head {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7.2vw, 6.4rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.022em;
  }
  .chapter-head em { font-style: italic; }
  .mega-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 14vw, 14rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-variant-numeric: lining-nums;
  }
  .kicker {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .copy-mono {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 42ch;
  }
  .copy-mono strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }
  .rule-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }

  /* Horizontal hairlines separating stat rows (hero score-strip style) */
  .rule-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .rule-row:first-of-type { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .rule-row .rr-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .rule-row .rr-value {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.4vw, 2.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ── Reveal system ── */
  .rev {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.3, 1), transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .rev.in { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .rev.d1 { transition-delay: 0.08s; }
  .rev.d2 { transition-delay: 0.18s; }
  .rev.d3 { transition-delay: 0.30s; }
  .rev.d4 { transition-delay: 0.42s; }
  .rev.d5 { transition-delay: 0.54s; }
  .rev.d6 { transition-delay: 0.68s; }

  /* Text mask-up reveal (for chapter heads) */
  .mask-up {
    display: inline-block;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mask-up > span {
    display: inline-block;
    transform: translateY(110%);
    transition: transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .mask-up.in > span { transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  header.hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100svh;
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vh, 7rem) clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem) clamp(2rem, 4vh, 4rem);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .hero-stage {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    min-height: 56vh;
  }
  /* Ghost serif "Pace." behind the subject */
  .hero-ghost-word {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    pointer-events: none;
    color: var(--ink-quiet);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(10rem, 30vw, 28rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    opacity: 0.35;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .hero-ghost-word em { font-style: italic; }
  /* Central subject visual — duotone soccer ball SVG cut out on black */
  .hero-subject {
    position: relative;
    width: clamp(18rem, 32vw, 30rem);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    z-index: 1;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.02);
  }
  .hero-subject svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }
  .hero-copy-top {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 0 clamp(1rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-copy-top > * { pointer-events: auto; }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.35rem);
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 14em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .hero-copy-main {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 44rem;
    align-self: end;
    padding: 0 clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 2rem);
  }
  .hero-lede {
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 48ch;
  }
  .hero-lede strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .hero-ctas {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5em;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: background 0.22s, color 0.22s, border-color 0.22s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .cta.primary {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .cta.primary:hover { background: transparent; color: var(--ink); }
  .cta.ghost {
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .cta.ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ink-mute); color: var(--ink); }
  .cta .arrow { transition: transform 0.22s ease; display: inline-block; }
  .cta:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }

  /* Hero bottom score-strip */
  .hero-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr auto;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    align-items: end;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .hs-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    max-width: 38rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .hs-top-kicker {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hs-footer-note {
    margin-top: 0.85rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .hs-right {
    text-align: right;
    padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .hs-mega {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 8vw, 8.5rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }
  .hs-mega em { font-style: italic; }
  .hs-mega-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .hero-copy-top { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .hero-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .hs-right { text-align: left; }
  }

  /* ── CHAPTER 2 · Ball-to-goal ── */
  .goal-stage {
    height: 260vh;
    position: relative;
  }
  .goal-sticky {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 5vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .goal-inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 80rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 3vh, 2rem);
    align-items: center;
    justify-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .goal-head { max-width: 22ch; margin: 0 auto; }
  .goal-scene {
    position: relative;
    width: min(100%, 52rem);
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 8;
  }
  .goal-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .goal-posts, .goal-net {
    stroke: var(--ink-mute);
    fill: none;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }
  .goal-posts { stroke-width: 2; stroke: var(--ink); opacity: 0.6; }
  .goal-net-vert, .goal-net-horiz {
    stroke: var(--ink-mute);
    stroke-width: 0.6;
    fill: none;
    opacity: 0.5;
    transform-origin: center top;
    transition: transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.3, 1);
  }
  body.warm-ground .goal-net-vert,
  body.warm-ground .goal-net-horiz { stroke: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.4); }
  /* When the ball lands, the net sways briefly */
  .goal-scene.ball-landed .goal-net-vert { transform: scaleY(1.03); }

  /* The ball */
  .ball {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(var(--ball-y, -22rem));
    width: clamp(3.2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    height: clamp(3.2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    will-change: transform;
    transition: transform 80ms linear;
  }
  .ball svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; filter: grayscale(1); }

  .goal-footer-note {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    max-width: 34rem;
  }

  /* ── CHAPTER 3 · Pace rotation (sticky) ── */
  .pace-stage {
    height: 440vh;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pace-sticky {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 4vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .pace-inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 84rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .pace-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  }

  .pace-left {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1.1 / 1;
    max-height: 72vh;
  }
  /* Ghost numeral hovers behind the tactical diagram (bam-83-style) */
  .pace-ghost-num {
    position: absolute;
    left: -1rem; bottom: -1rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(9rem, 22vw, 22rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    color: var(--ink-quiet);
    opacity: 0.55;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  /* Tactical pitch diagram */
  .pitch-svg {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .pitch-line {
    fill: none;
    stroke: var(--ink-mute);
    stroke-width: 1.2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
  }
  .pitch-dot {
    fill: var(--ink-quiet);
    transition: fill 0.55s ease, r 0.55s ease, opacity 0.55s ease;
  }
  .pitch-dot.active {
    fill: var(--ink);
    r: 7;
  }
  .pitch-dot.active.dominant-accent {
    fill: var(--accent);
  }
  .pitch-zone {
    fill: none;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    stroke-width: 1.2;
    stroke-dasharray: 3 3;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.55s ease;
  }
  .pitch-zone.active { opacity: 0.7; }

  .pace-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }
  .pace-kicker { letter-spacing: 0.28em; }
  .pace-num-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }
  .pace-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 12rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: color 0.5s ease;
  }
  .pace-num.accent-hit { color: var(--accent); }
  .pace-num-unit {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .pace-sub-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .pace-body {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 38ch;
    min-height: 5.5em;
    transition: opacity 0.28s ease;
  }
  .pace-body strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

  .pace-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem 1rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .pace-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    transition: color 0.35s ease;
  }
  .pace-stat-val {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 2.6vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .pace-stat-val.dominant { color: var(--accent); }
  .pace-stat-lab {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }

  /* Position ticker (where-are-we-in-the-rotation label, bottom of sticky) */
  .pace-progress-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 4vh;
    left: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .pace-progress-label .ppl-count {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ── CHAPTER 4 · Phone-video-to-proof scattered cards ── */
  .video-proof {
    min-height: 140vh;
    position: relative;
    padding: 10vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }
  .vp-intro {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 6rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .vp-intro .kicker { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .vp-intro h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 20ch; }
  .vp-intro p { margin-top: 1.2rem; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 50ch; }

  .vp-cards {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 82rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }
  .vp-card {
    background: rgba(240, 235, 225, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.6rem;
    max-width: 22rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .vp-card .vp-card-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.26em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .vp-card .vp-card-body {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .vp-card .vp-card-body strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .vp-card .vp-card-stat {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 1.1rem 0 0.3rem;
  }
  .vp-card .vp-card-stat-unit {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    margin-left: 0.3rem;
  }
  .vp-card.accent .vp-card-stat { color: var(--accent); }

  /* Absolute-positioned scatter across the chapter — asymmetric like bam quotes */
  .vp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem) clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .vp-grid .vp-card:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(-1rem); margin-left: 0.5rem; }
  .vp-grid .vp-card:nth-child(2) { transform: translateY(4.5rem); margin: 0 auto; }
  .vp-grid .vp-card:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(0.5rem); margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  .vp-grid .vp-card:nth-child(4) { transform: translateY(2.5rem); margin-left: 2rem; }
  .vp-grid .vp-card:nth-child(5) { transform: translateY(-1.5rem); margin: 0 auto; }
  .vp-grid .vp-card:nth-child(6) { transform: translateY(3rem); margin-right: 2rem; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .vp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .vp-grid .vp-card { transform: none !important; margin: 0 !important; }
  }

  /* ── CHAPTER 5 · Coach ── */
  .ch-coach {
    min-height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
    padding: 15vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .coach-inner {
    max-width: 84rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .coach-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
  .coach-text .kicker { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .coach-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 16ch; }
  .coach-text p { color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 42ch; }
  .coach-text p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

  /* Roster diagram — flat editorial, not a device shell */
  .coach-roster {
    position: relative;
  }
  .roster-wrap {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-left: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  }
  .roster-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .roster-head-kicker {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .roster-head-count {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .roster-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.2rem 1fr auto auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.05rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }
  .roster-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .roster-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ink-mute);
    justify-self: center;
  }
  .roster-dot.ok { background: var(--ink); }
  .roster-dot.warn { background: var(--accent); opacity: 0.7; }
  .roster-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .roster-role {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .roster-pace {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .roster-pace.warn { color: var(--accent); }

  /* ── CHAPTER 6 · Parent ── */
  .ch-parent {
    min-height: 90vh;
    padding: 15vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .parent-inner {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .parent-inner h2 { max-width: 20ch; }
  .parent-inner p { color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 46ch; text-align: center; }
  .parent-inner p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .parent-toggles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.05rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 26rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .parent-toggle {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.95rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .parent-toggle .pt-state {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 2.2rem;
    height: 1.05rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-mute);
    border-radius: 999px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .parent-toggle .pt-state::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 1px; left: 1px;
    width: calc(1.05rem - 4px);
    height: calc(1.05rem - 4px);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ink-mute);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease;
  }
  .parent-toggle.on .pt-state { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .parent-toggle.on .pt-state::before {
    background: var(--ink);
    transform: translateX(1.2rem);
  }

  /* ── CHAPTER 7 · Three roles strip ── */
  .ch-roles {
    min-height: 70vh;
    padding: 15vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    position: relative;
  }
  .roles-grid {
    max-width: 88rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .roles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
  .roles-col {
    padding: 0 clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 2.5rem);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .roles-col:first-child { border-left: none; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .roles-col { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 2rem 0 0; }
  }
  .roles-col h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .roles-col.primary h3 { font-style: italic; }
  .roles-col .kicker { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .roles-col p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
  }

  /* ── CHAPTER 8 · Closing CTA ── */
  .ch-close {
    min-height: 80vh;
    position: relative;
    padding: 15vh clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem) 12vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .close-inner {
    max-width: 52rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }
  .close-inner h2 { max-width: 18ch; }
  .close-inner .close-lede {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 42ch;
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .close-inner .close-lede strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .close-cta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .close-sig {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.2vw, 2.2rem);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  footer.foot {
    padding: 3rem clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  footer.foot .foot-logo {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  footer.foot .foot-logo em { font-style: italic; }
  footer.foot .foot-note {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }

  /* ── Chapter separator hairline ── */
  .chapter-rule {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--line);
    max-width: 80rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Reduced motion: degrade gracefully ── */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
    body { transition: none; }
    .rev { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; transition: none !important; }
    .mask-up > span { transform: translateY(0) !important; transition: none !important; }
    .scroll-badge .sb-ring { animation: none !important; }
    .ball { transition: none !important; }
    .goal-net-vert, .goal-net-horiz { transition: none !important; }
    .pace-num, .pace-stat-val { transition: none !important; }
    .pitch-dot, .pitch-zone { transition: none !important; }
    *, *::before, *::after {
      animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
      transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    }
  }

  /* Narrow viewport: disable some motion + layered flourishes */
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .scroll-badge { display: none; }
    .edge-pill { display: none; }
    .hero-ghost-word { opacity: 0.2; font-size: 50vw; }
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- Atmospheric overlays: grain + warm vignette -->
<div class="grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="vignette" aria-hidden="true"></div>

<!-- Floating circular "scroll" badge, top-left -->
<a href="#chapter-goal" class="scroll-badge" aria-label="Scroll to see the work" id="scrollBadge">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 92 92">
    <g class="sb-ring">
      <defs>
        <path id="sb-path" d="M 46 46 m -36 0 a 36 36 0 1 1 72 0 a 36 36 0 1 1 -72 0"/>
      </defs>
      <text><textPath href="#sb-path" startOffset="0">SCROLL TO SEE THE WORK · SCROLL TO SEE THE WORK · </textPath></text>
    </g>
    <line class="sb-arrow" x1="46" y1="39" x2="46" y2="53"/>
    <polyline class="sb-arrow" points="41,49 46,54 51,49"/>
  </svg>
</a>

<!-- Right-edge pill — persistent jump to pilot CTA -->
<a class="edge-pill" href="#pilot" aria-label="Pilot open · April 2026"><span class="pill-key">P.</span>Pilot</a>

<!-- Tiny top nav -->
<nav class="top" aria-label="Primary">
  <a class="logo" href="#top"><em>C</em>omposed</a>
  <a class="nav-contact" href="#pilot">Contact</a>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO — mega ghost serif + duotone ball + score-strip
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<header class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-stage">
    <div class="hero-ghost-word" aria-hidden="true"><em>Pace.</em></div>

    <div class="hero-copy-top">
      <p class="hero-tagline rev d1">Stay Composed.</p>
      <p class="kicker rev d2">Composed · 2026</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Duotone-rendered soccer ball (SVG, no external asset) -->
    <div class="hero-subject rev d2" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 300 300">
        <defs>
          <radialGradient id="ball-lit" cx="35%" cy="30%" r="70%">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f0ebe1"/>
            <stop offset="42%" stop-color="#a49e8f"/>
            <stop offset="75%" stop-color="#3a342a"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0b0907"/>
          </radialGradient>
          <filter id="ballgrain">
            <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="2.2" numOctaves="1" stitchTiles="stitch"/>
            <feColorMatrix values="0 0 0 0 0.94   0 0 0 0 0.92   0 0 0 0 0.88   0 0 0 0.35 0"/>
            <feComposite in2="SourceGraphic" operator="in"/>
          </filter>
        </defs>
        <circle cx="150" cy="150" r="138" fill="url(#ball-lit)"/>
        <circle cx="150" cy="150" r="138" fill="#000" opacity="0" filter="url(#ballgrain)"/>
        <!-- Pentagonal panel lines, classic ball -->
        <g stroke="#1a1714" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.78" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round">
          <polygon points="150,82 180,108 170,148 130,148 120,108" fill="#141210"/>
          <line x1="150" y1="82" x2="150" y2="38"/>
          <line x1="180" y1="108" x2="222" y2="96"/>
          <line x1="170" y1="148" x2="205" y2="180"/>
          <line x1="130" y1="148" x2="95" y2="180"/>
          <line x1="120" y1="108" x2="78" y2="96"/>
          <path d="M 95 180 Q 76 208 60 206" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M 205 180 Q 224 208 240 206" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M 78 96 Q 62 78 54 52" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M 222 96 Q 238 78 246 52" fill="none"/>
        </g>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-copy-main" style="grid-row: 1;">
    <h1 class="display-hero rev d3">
      Stop Guessing.<br><span class="serif-it">Start Proving.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-lede rev d4">
      The hours you put in alone — in the backyard, on the wall, in the empty park — <strong>finally count.</strong>
      Real measurement for youth players who train between team sessions.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas rev d5">
      <a class="cta primary" href="#chapter-goal">See how it works <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      <a class="cta ghost" href="#pilot">For coaches</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Score-strip (bam83 grammar: label | stat rows + mega numeral right) -->
  <div class="hero-strip rev d6">
    <div class="hs-left">
      <div class="hs-top-kicker kicker">Youth soccer · Position-weighted</div>
      <div class="rule-row"><span class="rr-label">Pre-launch · pilot open</span><span class="rr-value">April 2026</span></div>
      <div class="rule-row"><span class="rr-label">Position weight tables</span><span class="rr-value">6</span></div>
      <div class="rule-row"><span class="rr-label">Roles supported</span><span class="rr-value">3</span></div>
      <p class="hs-footer-note">Player · Coach · Parent · Parent visibility player-controlled</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hs-right">
      <div class="hs-mega"><em>Pace.</em></div>
      <div class="hs-mega-label">Position-weighted improvement velocity</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<hr class="chapter-rule" aria-hidden="true">

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     CHAPTER 2 — BALL INTO GOAL (sticky, scroll-bound, dark→brass reveal)
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="goal-stage" id="chapter-goal" data-chapter="goal">
  <div class="goal-sticky">
    <div class="goal-inner">
      <p class="kicker rev" data-reveal>Chapter one · The work</p>
      <h2 class="chapter-head goal-head">
        <span class="mask-up"><span>The work nobody</span></span><br>
        <span class="mask-up"><span><em>can see.</em> Yet.</span></span>
      </h2>
      <div class="goal-scene" id="goalScene">
        <svg class="goal-svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 500" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMax meet">
          <!-- Goal frame -->
          <g class="goal-posts">
            <!-- Posts + crossbar as one rounded rectangle opening -->
            <line x1="180" y1="70" x2="180" y2="360"/>
            <line x1="820" y1="70" x2="820" y2="360"/>
            <line x1="180" y1="70" x2="820" y2="70"/>
            <!-- Ground line -->
            <line x1="80" y1="360" x2="920" y2="360" stroke-width="1.3" opacity="0.4"/>
          </g>
          <!-- Net: vertical lines -->
          <g id="netVerts">
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="200" y1="72" x2="220" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="240" y1="72" x2="260" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="290" y1="72" x2="302" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="340" y1="72" x2="346" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="390" y1="72" x2="392" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="440" y1="72" x2="438" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="490" y1="72" x2="484" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="540" y1="72" x2="532" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="590" y1="72" x2="580" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="640" y1="72" x2="628" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="690" y1="72" x2="676" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="740" y1="72" x2="722" y2="358"/>
            <line class="goal-net-vert" x1="780" y1="72" x2="760" y2="358"/>
          </g>
          <!-- Net: horizontal lines -->
          <g id="netHoriz">
            <line class="goal-net-horiz" x1="185" y1="130" x2="815" y2="130"/>
            <line class="goal-net-horiz" x1="192" y1="180" x2="808" y2="180"/>
            <line class="goal-net-horiz" x1="198" y1="230" x2="802" y2="230"/>
            <line class="goal-net-horiz" x1="205" y1="280" x2="795" y2="280"/>
            <line class="goal-net-horiz" x1="210" y1="330" x2="790" y2="330"/>
          </g>
          <!-- Field mark: central penalty spot as subtle reference -->
          <circle cx="500" cy="360" r="3" fill="var(--ink-mute)" opacity="0.3"/>
        </svg>

        <!-- Ball — positioned absolutely, Y-bound to scroll -->
        <div class="ball" id="ball">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100">
            <defs>
              <radialGradient id="ball2-lit" cx="32%" cy="28%" r="78%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#f0ebe1"/>
                <stop offset="48%" stop-color="#958d7c"/>
                <stop offset="85%" stop-color="#2a251d"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a0806"/>
              </radialGradient>
            </defs>
            <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="46" fill="url(#ball2-lit)"/>
            <g stroke="#141210" stroke-width="1.1" fill="none" opacity="0.8" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="50,28 60,37 56,50 44,50 40,37" fill="#100e0b"/>
              <line x1="50" y1="28" x2="50" y2="12"/>
              <line x1="60" y1="37" x2="72" y2="32"/>
              <line x1="56" y1="50" x2="66" y2="60"/>
              <line x1="44" y1="50" x2="34" y2="60"/>
              <line x1="40" y1="37" x2="28" y2="32"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="goal-footer-note rev" data-reveal>
        Training between team sessions. Backyard repetitions.
        The work that gets noticed when the goal gets scored — not before.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="chapter-rule" aria-hidden="true">

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     CHAPTER 3 — PACE (sticky scroll-bound rotation through 4 positions)
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="pace-stage" id="chapter-pace">
  <div class="pace-sticky">
    <div class="pace-inner">
      <!-- Left: tactical pitch diagram with ghost numeral behind -->
      <div class="pace-left">
        <div class="pace-ghost-num" id="paceGhostNum">1</div>
        <svg class="pitch-svg" viewBox="0 0 600 520" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
          <!-- Half-pitch outline (vertical orientation) -->
          <g class="pitch-line">
            <!-- Outer -->
            <rect x="60" y="30" width="480" height="460" rx="4" fill="none"/>
            <!-- Centerline (top edge of half-pitch we're showing) -->
            <line x1="60" y1="30" x2="540" y2="30"/>
            <!-- 18-yard box -->
            <rect x="180" y="360" width="240" height="130" fill="none"/>
            <!-- 6-yard box -->
            <rect x="240" y="430" width="120" height="60" fill="none"/>
            <!-- Penalty arc -->
            <path d="M 260 360 A 40 40 0 0 0 340 360" fill="none"/>
            <!-- Penalty spot -->
            <circle cx="300" cy="400" r="2" fill="var(--ink-mute)"/>
            <!-- Center circle (partial, top of viewport) -->
            <path d="M 255 30 A 45 45 0 0 0 345 30" fill="none"/>
          </g>

          <!-- Role-zone highlights (toggled per position) -->
          <g id="pitchZones">
            <!-- Striker: attacking third, inside 18-yard box -->
            <path class="pitch-zone" data-zone="Striker" d="M 200 380 h 200 v 100 h -200 z" />
            <!-- Winger: wide attacking channels -->
            <path class="pitch-zone" data-zone="Winger" d="M 80 180 h 80 v 280 h -80 z M 440 180 h 80 v 280 h -80 z" />
            <!-- CAM: between lines, arc-adjacent -->
            <path class="pitch-zone" data-zone="CAM" d="M 220 280 h 160 v 110 h -160 z" />
            <!-- CDM: deeper midfield -->
            <path class="pitch-zone" data-zone="CDM" d="M 200 140 h 200 v 110 h -200 z" />
            <!-- CB: defensive third -->
            <path class="pitch-zone" data-zone="CB" d="M 170 40 h 260 v 90 h -260 z" />
            <!-- GK: inside 6-yard -->
            <path class="pitch-zone" data-zone="GK" d="M 240 430 h 120 v 60 h -120 z" />
          </g>

          <!-- Position dots: one per role, fixed position on pitch, light up when active -->
          <g id="pitchDots">
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="Striker" data-dom="shooting" cx="300" cy="430" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="Winger" data-dom="load" cx="120" cy="320" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="Winger-r" data-dom="load" cx="480" cy="320" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="CAM" data-dom="passing" cx="300" cy="335" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="CDM" data-dom="passing" cx="300" cy="195" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="CB" data-dom="passing" cx="240" cy="85" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="CB-r" data-dom="passing" cx="360" cy="85" r="5"/>
            <circle class="pitch-dot" data-pos="GK" data-dom="load" cx="300" cy="465" r="5"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: stat block with headline, number, body, 3-stat row -->
      <div class="pace-right">
        <div class="pace-kicker kicker" id="paceKicker">What is Pace</div>
        <div class="pace-num-line">
          <div class="pace-num" id="paceNum">—</div>
          <div class="pace-num-unit">%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pace-sub-label" id="paceSubLabel">Improvement velocity · weekly</div>
        <p class="pace-body" id="paceBody">
          Pace measures the <strong>rate of your improvement</strong> — week over week, session over session.
          It's not where you are. It's where you're going. And it's weighted to the position you play.
        </p>
        <div class="pace-stats" id="paceStats">
          <div class="pace-stat" data-metric="shooting"><span class="pace-stat-val">20%</span><span class="pace-stat-lab">Shooting</span></div>
          <div class="pace-stat" data-metric="passing"><span class="pace-stat-val">20%</span><span class="pace-stat-lab">Passing</span></div>
          <div class="pace-stat" data-metric="consistency"><span class="pace-stat-val">20%</span><span class="pace-stat-lab">Consistency</span></div>
          <div class="pace-stat" data-metric="duration"><span class="pace-stat-val">20%</span><span class="pace-stat-lab">Duration</span></div>
          <div class="pace-stat" data-metric="load"><span class="pace-stat-val">20%</span><span class="pace-stat-lab">Load</span></div>
          <div class="pace-stat"><span class="pace-stat-val">—</span><span class="pace-stat-lab">Position</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pace-progress-label" aria-hidden="true">
      <span id="paceProgressIndex" class="ppl-count">01</span>
      <span>of 07 · <span id="paceProgressLabel">Default model</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="chapter-rule" aria-hidden="true">

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     CHAPTER 4 — VIDEO TO PROOF (scattered evidence cards)
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="video-proof" id="chapter-video">
  <div class="vp-intro rev" data-reveal>
    <div class="kicker">Chapter three · Phone video into proof</div>
    <h2 class="chapter-head">
      <span>Your camera roll</span><br>
      <span class="serif-it">becomes the record.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="copy-mono">
      No smart ball. No tripod. No device ecosystem to buy into. You record a drill on your phone the way you already do —
      and the video becomes <strong>real stats</strong>, counted and confirmable, before it ever leaves the device.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="vp-cards">
    <div class="vp-grid">
      <div class="vp-card rev" data-reveal data-delay="0">
        <div class="vp-card-tag">Record · from the phone</div>
        <div class="vp-card-body">
          Up to 500 MB · MP4 · MOV · WebM · AVI. Drop the clip on the page or pick from camera roll. <strong>Nothing is sent yet.</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card-stat">4<span class="vp-card-stat-unit">formats</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="vp-card accent rev" data-reveal data-delay="120">
        <div class="vp-card-tag">Compress · in the app</div>
        <div class="vp-card-body">
          <strong>FFmpeg.wasm</strong> transcodes to 720p H.264 on-device. Nothing about your session touches a server until you choose to log it.
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card-stat">720<span class="vp-card-stat-unit">p · client-side</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="vp-card rev" data-reveal data-delay="240">
        <div class="vp-card-tag">Extract · key frames</div>
        <div class="vp-card-body">
          10 to 50 frames pulled per minute of footage. Enough for a model to read the movement without draining the phone battery.
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card-stat">10–50<span class="vp-card-stat-unit">frames/min</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="vp-card rev" data-reveal data-delay="80">
        <div class="vp-card-tag">Count · frame by frame</div>
        <div class="vp-card-body">
          Shots, goals, left- and right-foot splits, pass attempts — <strong>read off the video</strong>, not typed in after the fact.
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card-stat">5<span class="vp-card-stat-unit">metric types</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="vp-card rev" data-reveal data-delay="200">
        <div class="vp-card-tag">Pre-fill · the session form</div>
        <div class="vp-card-body">
          Every count drops into a draft session log. You see exactly what the model counted, alongside the raw numbers.
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card-stat">14 / 8 / 3<span class="vp-card-stat-unit">shots · on-target · goals</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="vp-card rev" data-reveal data-delay="320">
        <div class="vp-card-tag">Confirm · before it saves</div>
        <div class="vp-card-body">
          You <strong>edit anything that's off</strong>. You tap confirm. Only then does it become part of your Pace. The model assists; it doesn't author.
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card-stat">You<span class="vp-card-stat-unit">own the save</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="chapter-rule" aria-hidden="true">

